== Install & Usage

currently, please useing python setuptools to install.

	user@hsot# sudo ./setup install

run with graphic 

	user@host# glzs

run with graphic and sync scripts by auto.

	user@host# glzs --sync

run with last selection 

	user@host# glzs --selection last_selection.ini

